<% layout('./layout') -%>

<div class='headline center-block'>
    <img src='/images/logo-big.png' class='img-responsive' alt="Books 4 Equality">
    <p class='lead'>Your Free Textbook Library</p>
</div>

<div class='jumbotron'>
    <p class='lead'>
        Books4Equality aims to provide equal access to textbooks for everyone. For FREE!
    </p>
    <p>We lend you books for the semester at no cost, so you can focus on classes.</p>

    <div class='sub-section'>
        <h4 class='cent'>It's Collection Time!</h4>
        <h6>Donate your books</h6>
        <p>As finals appreach, we'll be collecting books to for the fall<p>
        <ol>
            <li>If you borrowed a book, we want it back</li>
            <li>If you have textbooks to donate, we'd love to take them off your hands</li>
        </ol>
        <h6>When?</h6>
        <p>10-2 PM Weekdays May 5th-13th</p>
        <h6>Where?</h6>
        <p>Outside the Bailey/Howe Library</p>
    </div>

    <div class='sub-section'>
        <h4>Bands 4 Equality Block Party</h4>

        <strong>May 4th 2016, 3 PM - 7 PM, Redstone Campus</strong>
        <p>Watch some stellar performances by MELON, Doctor Rick, Chosin, Catamount Dance Crew, The UVM Cat's Meow, and DAUT!! Games, activities, and give-aways. B4E will be collecting textbooks and iClickers for UVM students next year!</p></p>
        <p><a href="https://www.facebook.com/events/171624526564404/">Sign up for the event on FaceBook</a></p>
        <img src="images/home/2016/bands-4-equality.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="Bands 4 Equality">
    </div>



